data.description: OPEN HOUSE 1/27 & 1/28 FROM 2-4PM!!!   Welcome to 408 Whitworth Ct! This adorable ranch boasts 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms on .22 acres in a cul de sac with NO HOA. As you walk in you'll notice the wide foyer that leads to the open concept kitchen, dining, and living room perfect for entertaining. This home offers a split bedroom plan with two bedrooms with a shared full bath on the left side of the home and then owner's suite on the right side of the home. Upstairs you will find a room with a closet for storage that could be used as the 4th bedroom, an office, or a playroom. Back downstairs you'll walk out the back door to a nice size fenced in yard. Don't miss out on this DISTRICT 5 home, schedule a tour today!!
